title: American Horror Story: Double Feature | KPCD 666 CAPE RADIO: CHAPTER 2 - Season 10 | FX
author: FX Networks
comment: Tune in for the latest hits.

You can really tell who the OG fans of AHS are because this is giving classic AHS vibes and I'm loving it. But I can also see where newer fans would not be a fan of these random teasers and world-building. We are finally going back to the og roots of AHS!! This season gonna hit different!!
I can’t wait til this all makes sense tomorrow when it comes out

Interesting things I've picked up from Chapter 2:

Rose is sick in chapter 2, but not chapter 1. Is something spreading in Provincetown?
Starts with classical violin music (Alma plays violin)

This is simply revolutionary and genuis storytelling while giving and paying such throwback homage AM Golden Age of Radio vibes to older generations....Ryan outdoes himself over and over...I'm just in awe and completely inspired!!
description:
You’re listening to KPCD 666 Cape Radio. Talk, news, and local tunes from the tip of Route 6.
